1
00:00:02,293 --> 00:00:04,713
<i>[Max] </i>Michiko, how's our accounting?

2
00:00:04,796 --> 00:00:06,214
<i>[Michiko] It's already done, Max.</i>

3
00:00:06,297 --> 00:00:08,842
<i>Wait, don't I owe you money for our food?</i>

4
00:00:08,925 --> 00:00:10,093
<i>How much was it?</i>

5
00:00:10,176 --> 00:00:11,261
<i>[Michiko] Eight hundred.</i>

6
00:00:11,344 --> 00:00:14,389
<i>Are you serious?</i>
<i>Eight hundred just for that?</i>

7
00:00:14,472 --> 00:00:16,099
<i>Yeah, but don't worry about it, Max.</i>

8
00:00:16,182 --> 00:00:17,517
<i>Deib already paid for it.</i>

9
00:00:19,477 --> 00:00:21,479
<i>No. I'm going to pay you back.</i>

10
00:00:21,563 --> 00:00:24,315
<i>No need, Max. It's my treat.</i>

11
00:00:24,399 --> 00:00:27,027
<i>I don't want to owe you anything.</i>
<i>I'll pay for it, okay?</i>

12
00:00:27,110 --> 00:00:30,405
<i>Max, just take the money</i>
<i>and say thank you.</i>

13
00:00:30,488 --> 00:00:33,116
<i>Okay. Thank you.</i>
<i>But I'm still gonna pay for that.</i>

14
00:00:33,199 --> 00:00:35,452
<i>No. You don't have to, okay?</i>

15
00:00:35,535 --> 00:00:38,163
<i>[Lorde] Madam Max,</i>
<i>give me the money instead.</i>

16
00:00:38,246 --> 00:00:40,832
<i>Master has never treated me--</i>

17
00:00:40,915 --> 00:00:41,750
<i>Lorde!</i>

18
00:00:41,833 --> 00:00:44,169
<i>[Lorde] Why are you treating Max?</i>

19
00:00:44,252 --> 00:00:45,503
<i>Because!</i>

20
00:00:46,254 --> 00:00:47,505
<i>That's what friends do!</i>

21
00:00:47,589 --> 00:00:49,090
<i>[scoffs] Friends.</i>

22
00:00:49,174 --> 00:00:51,968
<i>[Lorde] Friends? I'm your friend too!</i>

23
00:00:52,052 --> 00:00:55,055
<i>Not as special as Max, though.</i>

24
00:00:55,680 --> 00:00:56,890
<i>[Tob] Shut up, Lorde!</i>

25
00:00:58,058 --> 00:01:01,352
<i>Could you not? Quit teasing us!</i>

26
00:01:01,436 --> 00:01:03,313
<i>He doesn't like me, okay?</i>

27
00:01:03,396 --> 00:01:05,148
<i>You were just joking, right?</i>

28
00:01:07,192 --> 00:01:08,026
<i>Yes!</i>

29
00:01:09,069 --> 00:01:12,405
<i>Even that thing about us being friends,</i>
<i>that was just a joke!</i>

30
00:01:13,239 --> 00:01:16,493
<i>Really? So you really don't trust me?</i>

31
00:01:16,576 --> 00:01:18,661
<i>[Deib] After everything</i>
<i>we've been through,</i>

32
00:01:18,745 --> 00:01:20,705
<i>you think we still aren't friends?</i>

33
00:01:20,789 --> 00:01:24,667
<i>How the hell would I know</i>
<i>if we're really friends?</i>

34
00:01:25,418 --> 00:01:27,670
<i>For all I know,</i>
<i>this is just another prank!</i>

35
00:01:27,754 --> 00:01:29,756
<i>Why is it so hard to believe</i>
<i>that I've changed?</i>

36
00:01:29,839 --> 00:01:32,425
<i>Because you're confusing as hell!</i>
<i>I don't know what to believe!</i>

37
00:01:32,509 --> 00:01:33,802
<i>You say we're friends?</i>

38
00:01:33,885 --> 00:01:37,680
<i>But whenever I'm honest about how I feel,</i>
<i>which a friend should be,</i>

39
00:01:37,764 --> 00:01:39,516
<i>you get pissed off!</i>

40
00:01:40,558 --> 00:01:43,853
<i>Fine! If you don't want to be my friend,</i>
<i>then we're not friends!</i>

41
00:01:45,230 --> 00:01:48,108
<i>[somber music playing]</i>

42
00:01:50,944 --> 00:01:53,947
<i>Oh no!</i>

43
00:01:54,030 --> 00:01:55,990
<i>Are we gonna go back</i>
<i>to the way things were?</i>

44
00:01:56,074 --> 00:01:58,660
<i>No! No! No! I cannot!</i>

45
00:02:00,745 --> 00:02:01,955
<i>Max.</i>

46
00:02:11,506 --> 00:02:15,718
<i>JONALYN: WHAT IS THIS FQ</i>
<i>BETWEEN MAX &amp; DEIB?</i>

47
00:02:21,850 --> 00:02:24,394
<i>She still sees me as someone</i>
<i>who will hurt her.</i>

48
00:02:26,020 --> 00:02:30,567
<i>It's tiring having to prove yourself</i>
<i>over and over again.</i>

49
00:02:35,947 --> 00:02:37,448
<i>But then again, it's my fault.</i>

50
00:02:40,660 --> 00:02:42,996
<i>Maybe I really do hurt the people I love.</i>

51
00:02:47,167 --> 00:02:48,251
<i>[notification dings]</i>

52
00:02:50,670 --> 00:02:55,717
<i>[woman narrates text]</i>

