<i>♪ He's into her ♪</i>

71
00:04:04,369 --> 00:04:05,828
<i>♪ Into her ♪</i>

72
00:04:05,912 --> 00:04:06,871
<i>[music ends]</i>

73
00:04:07,664 --> 00:04:12,460
<i>[Naih] Girl, why did you say</i>
<i>that you and Deib are not friends?</i>

74
00:04:12,543 --> 00:04:13,795
<i>I feel bad for him.</i>

75
00:04:13,878 --> 00:04:16,923
<i>Maybe she wants to be</i>
<i>more than just friends with him?</i>

76
00:04:17,006 --> 00:04:20,218
<i>If you're just gonna tease me,</i>
<i>just go away.</i>

77
00:04:20,885 --> 00:04:24,973
<i>But Max, it looks like Deib really wants</i>
<i>to be friends with you.</i>

78
00:04:25,056 --> 00:04:26,849
<i>Why don't you give him a chance?</i>

79
00:04:26,933 --> 00:04:29,769
<i>Friendship isn't something</i>
<i>you impose on others.</i>

80
00:04:29,852 --> 00:04:31,020
<i>It just happens.</i>

81
00:04:31,104 --> 00:04:32,146
<i>[Ysay] Like love.</i>

82
00:04:32,230 --> 00:04:34,607
<i>You and Deib were so cute the other night.</i>

83
00:04:34,691 --> 00:04:38,278
<i>[Ysay] I felt like I was</i>
<i>watching a manga love story.</i>

84
00:04:38,361 --> 00:04:39,946
<i>The way Deib tried to court you--</i>

85
00:04:40,029 --> 00:04:42,240
<i>But he's not courting me.</i>

86
00:04:43,241 --> 00:04:45,535
<i>How sure are you, girl?</i>

87
00:04:45,618 --> 00:04:48,621
<i>[Naih] Has someone courted you before?</i>
<i>Have you had a boyfriend?</i>

88
00:04:49,330 --> 00:04:53,126
<i>Hey! Look at that smile. Spill the tea!</i>

89
00:04:53,209 --> 00:04:55,253
<i>[all] Girl…</i>

90
00:04:55,336 --> 00:04:56,671
<i>That smile is full of mystery.</i>

91
00:04:56,754 --> 00:05:01,384
<i>Yes, I've been in love before.</i>
<i>And someone loved me.</i>

92
00:05:02,260 --> 00:05:04,429
<i>[inaudible murmuring]</i>

93
00:05:06,180 --> 00:05:08,933
<i>[Max]</i> I was seven years old
when I met him.

94
00:05:09,642 --> 00:05:11,311
<i>His name was RJ.</i>

95
00:05:12,729 --> 00:05:16,649
<i>From then onwards, we were best friends.</i>

96
00:05:17,525 --> 00:05:18,484
<i>Hi!</i>

97
00:05:19,235 --> 00:05:20,987
<i>-Hi!</i>
<i>-Do you wanna play?</i>

98
00:05:21,070 --> 00:05:22,280
<i>There are no other kids.</i>

99
00:05:24,073 --> 00:05:25,408
<i>Okay.</i>

100
00:05:25,491 --> 00:05:26,534
<i>Let's go.</i>

101
00:05:26,617 --> 00:05:29,662
<i>[Max]</i> Even though we only saw each other
during summer breaks

102
00:05:29,746 --> 00:05:31,456
<i>when he'd come home from Manila.</i>

103
00:05:41,758 --> 00:05:45,928
<i>Max! That photo might melt</i>
<i>from all that staring.</i>

104
00:05:47,430 --> 00:05:49,515
<i>I just miss this dude so much.</i>

105
00:05:50,141 --> 00:05:52,435
<i>[Bhaves] Don't worry. It's almost summer.</i>

106
00:05:52,518 --> 00:05:54,604
<i>You'll be seeing each other again.</i>

107
00:05:54,687 --> 00:05:56,230
<i>-[chuckles]</i>
<i>-[phone rings]</i>

108
00:05:58,941 --> 00:06:01,110
<i>Hey! Hello! I thought you'd never call!</i>

109
00:06:01,944 --> 00:06:05,114
<i>When are you coming home? You promised</i>
<i>you'd teach me to play billiards!</i>

110
00:06:12,330 --> 00:06:13,623
<i>[Max]</i> At that time,

111
00:06:13,706 --> 00:06:16,084
<i>he told me that if I beat him</i>
<i>at billiards,</i>

112
00:06:16,167 --> 00:06:18,044
<i>he would court me.</i>

113
00:06:22,131 --> 00:06:23,299
<i>I won.</i>

114
00:06:25,468 --> 00:06:26,511
<i>[chuckles]</i>

115
00:06:27,678 --> 00:06:29,847
<i>[Max]</i> Maybe I really wanted him
to court me.

116
00:06:30,973 --> 00:06:33,351
<i>He wooed me that whole summer.</i>

117
00:06:34,060 --> 00:06:35,978
<i>He made my whole family</i>
<i>fall in love with him too.</i>

118
00:06:36,562 --> 00:06:41,234
<i>-RJ, are you already in love with her?</i>
<i>-</i>I loved that he even loved my family.

119
00:06:41,984 --> 00:06:44,487
<i>It feels wonderful to be loved by someone</i>

120
00:06:45,738 --> 00:06:47,115
<i>who really sees you,</i>

121
00:06:47,990 --> 00:06:52,120
<i>and who wants to do everything</i>
<i>to make you happy.</i>

122
00:06:53,371 --> 00:06:55,581
<i>On his last night in Mindoro,</i>

123
00:06:55,665 --> 00:06:58,209
<i>he asked me to be his girlfriend.</i>

124
00:07:01,254 --> 00:07:03,297
<i>There was only one answer-- yes.</i>

125
00:07:05,925 --> 00:07:07,927
<i>And because I loved him,</i>

126
00:07:08,010 --> 00:07:10,096
<i>I believed we could conquer all.</i>

127
00:07:10,179 --> 00:07:11,848
<i>HOW'S LIFE THERE IN THE STATES?</i>

128
00:07:11,931 --> 00:07:13,266
<i>HOW'S SCHOOL?</i>

129
00:07:13,349 --> 00:07:15,435
<i>HOW'S YOUR DAD DOING?</i>

130
00:07:15,518 --> 00:07:19,272
<i>LET'S COMMUNICATE VIA E-MAIL.</i>

131
00:07:19,355 --> 00:07:22,733
<i>[Max]</i> But he became more distant
when he got a full-time scholarship

132
00:07:22,817 --> 00:07:24,986
<i>in the US to play basketball.</i>

133
00:07:26,112 --> 00:07:27,738
<i>I was so happy for him…</i>

134
00:07:32,368 --> 00:07:33,578
<i>"Hi Babu…"</i>

135
00:07:34,579 --> 00:07:37,248
<i>[Max]</i> As much as I wanted
to believe that nothing had changed,

136
00:07:37,331 --> 00:07:39,125
<i>that nothing would change,</i>

137
00:07:39,876 --> 00:07:41,085
<i>something did change.</i>

138
00:07:42,336 --> 00:07:44,172
<i>He suddenly went silent.</i>

139
00:07:45,590 --> 00:07:47,175
<i>He just disappeared.</i>

140
00:07:48,301 --> 00:07:49,886
<i>And it hurt.</i>

141
00:07:51,095 --> 00:07:53,097
<i>The worst part of it was</i>

142
00:07:53,181 --> 00:07:55,975
<i>he wasn't there when I really needed him.</i>

143
00:07:57,018 --> 00:07:58,895
<i>Dear Babu--</i>

144
00:08:00,563 --> 00:08:01,981
<i>[keyboard tapping]</i>

145
00:08:02,064 --> 00:08:04,609
<i>Dear RJ--</i>

146
00:08:08,654 --> 00:08:09,530
<i>RJ!</i>

147
00:08:10,239 --> 00:08:12,283
<i>Are you angry?</i>

148
00:08:15,036 --> 00:08:17,038
<i>Have I done something wrong?</i>

149
00:08:22,376 --> 00:08:23,586
<i>Are we over?</i>

150
00:08:29,884 --> 00:08:30,927
<i>[sighs]</i>

151
00:08:32,803 --> 00:08:34,388
<i>Answer me.</i>

152
00:08:35,306 --> 00:08:36,557
<i>Please!</i>

153
00:08:41,062 --> 00:08:44,148
<i>[sad music plays]</i>

154
00:08:55,243 --> 00:08:57,995
<i>[sad music continues]</i>

155
00:09:05,461 --> 00:09:06,462
<i>[sighs]</i>

156
00:09:13,135 --> 00:09:14,512
<i>[Boyet]</i> <i>Watch your step, Ma.</i>

157
00:09:14,595 --> 00:09:16,305
<i>Just stay here, Max.</i>

158
00:09:17,265 --> 00:09:18,891
<i>[Max] I'm going with you, Uncle!</i>

159
00:09:19,392 --> 00:09:20,518
<i>[Boyet] No, Max.</i>

160
00:09:20,601 --> 00:09:23,396
<i>Just stay here, and study</i>
<i>for your exam tomorrow.</i>

161
00:09:23,479 --> 00:09:25,147
<i>You have to pass that test.</i>

162
00:09:25,231 --> 00:09:26,816
<i>I'll take care of your Grandma.</i>

163
00:09:27,984 --> 00:09:29,443
<i>Please be careful, Uncle.</i>

164
00:09:29,527 --> 00:09:31,696
<i>Please update me</i>
<i>when you get to the hospital.</i>

165
00:09:31,779 --> 00:09:33,906
<i>Uncle, take care of Grams--</i>

166
00:09:34,490 --> 00:09:36,826
<i>-Be careful. You'll be okay, Grandma.</i>
<i>-[Boyet] Okay, Max.</i>

167
00:09:36,909 --> 00:09:39,287
<i>-[Boyet] I can handle this.</i>
<i>-Text me right away.</i>

168
00:09:40,663 --> 00:09:42,039
<i>Careful on your way there.</i>

169
00:09:44,250 --> 00:09:48,379
<i>[Max]</i> Grandma got sick soon
after RJ left for the US.

170
00:09:49,005 --> 00:09:51,007
<i>After that, our debts piled up.</i>

171
00:09:52,008 --> 00:09:55,094
<i>I even told Uncle Boyet</i>
<i>to stop sending me to school.</i>

172
00:09:55,177 --> 00:09:58,306
<i>But he wouldn't agree.</i>
<i>I could see he was having a hard time.</i>

173
00:09:59,265 --> 00:10:02,268
<i>That's why when the opportunity</i>
<i>to study here came--</i>

174
00:10:02,351 --> 00:10:05,855
<i>Your other uncle, Elle's dad--</i>

175
00:10:05,938 --> 00:10:10,693
<i>Uh… yeah. I grabbed it right away, even</i>
<i>if it meant being away from my family.</i>

176
00:10:10,776 --> 00:10:12,403
<i>I don't want to be a liability.</i>

177
00:10:13,237 --> 00:10:16,073
<i>I want my family</i>
<i>to be proud of me someday.</i>

178
00:10:16,824 --> 00:10:18,868
<i>So, do you get it now?</i>

179
00:10:18,951 --> 00:10:20,828
<i>I don't have time for silly romances.</i>

180
00:10:20,911 --> 00:10:23,914
<i>Boys are such big headaches.</i>
<i>They all leave you heartbroken.</i>

181
00:10:23,998 --> 00:10:25,291
<i>If I were you, guys,</i>

182
00:10:25,374 --> 00:10:28,586
<i>I'd just focus on my studies</i>
<i>so I had a good future.</i>

183
00:10:28,669 --> 00:10:31,839
<i>So you have no idea where he is now?</i>

184
00:10:32,840 --> 00:10:35,509
<i>No idea. Maybe he found someone prettier.</i>

185
00:10:35,593 --> 00:10:37,887
<i>Look at me. I've got nothing on</i>
<i>those girls from over there.</i>

186
00:10:37,970 --> 00:10:40,348
<i>All I know is he's not coming back here.</i>

187
00:10:40,431 --> 00:10:42,516
<i>I don't think he remembers me.</i>
<i>Probably a big shot now.</i>

188
00:10:43,100 --> 00:10:44,185
<i>But you still love him?</i>

189
00:10:44,268 --> 00:10:46,812
<i>I'm gonna punch him when I see him.</i>

190
00:10:46,896 --> 00:10:49,148
<i>That's not a straight answer.</i>

191
00:10:49,231 --> 00:10:50,316
<i>-Too showbiz.</i>
<i>-[Naih] True.</i>

192
00:10:50,399 --> 00:10:53,194
<i>I'm over him. I'm done with love.</i>

193
00:10:53,277 --> 00:10:54,528
<i>I believe you're over him</i>

194
00:10:54,612 --> 00:10:58,115
<i>because I'm a TagSen shipper now.</i>

195
00:10:58,783 --> 00:10:59,784
<i>[Ysay] Look!</i>

196
00:10:59,867 --> 00:11:02,787
<i>-[Naih] Nice!</i>
<i>-[Migz] Wow!</i>

197
00:11:03,412 --> 00:11:04,330
<i>[Naih] Perfect, sis!</i>

198
00:11:04,413 --> 00:11:07,917
<i>So, please. Just give Deib another chance!</i>

199
00:11:08,000 --> 00:11:12,463
<i>No! Enrile is just playing me.</i>

200
00:11:12,546 --> 00:11:15,925
<i>He's just like RJ. He just led me on!</i>

201
00:11:16,008 --> 00:11:19,720
<i>I refuse to be another casualty</i>
<i>of this foolishness called love.</i>

202
00:11:19,804 --> 00:11:21,806
<i>But girl, open your heart</i>

203
00:11:21,889 --> 00:11:24,058
<i>because he's giving you the signs.</i>

204
00:11:24,141 --> 00:11:25,017
<i>[Ysay] True.</i>

205
00:11:25,101 --> 00:11:26,185
<i>Correct!</i>

206
00:11:26,268 --> 00:11:30,898
<i>[Barb] I'm also giving you the sign</i>
<i>to stop disrupting Max's work! Work!</i>

207
00:11:30,981 --> 00:11:32,733
<i>[Naih chuckles]</i>

208
00:11:38,531 --> 00:11:40,032
<i>Okay. Closing time.</i>

209
00:11:43,953 --> 00:11:45,746
<i>[Barb] Wait. I think we have</i>
<i>more customers.</i>

210
00:11:45,830 --> 00:11:47,998
<i>Okay. We're gonna open again</i>
<i>for these handsome boys!</i>

211
00:11:49,750 --> 00:11:51,544
<i>Madam Barbs, let's just close now!</i>

212
00:11:52,670 --> 00:11:55,798
<i>Why? As your friend said, open your heart.</i>
<i>Let's keep The Barb open too.</i>

213
00:11:56,424 --> 00:11:58,718
<i>No. It's time to close.</i>
<i>It's time to move on.</i>

214
00:11:59,427 --> 00:12:01,220
<i>Max is right. We have to close now.</i>

215
00:12:01,303 --> 00:12:02,680
<i>We have to move on.</i>

216
00:12:05,307 --> 00:12:06,976
<i>Besides, they're our enemies</i>
<i>from Southbay!</i>

217
00:12:09,353 --> 00:12:11,939
<i>[pensive music playing]</i>

218
00:12:18,070 --> 00:12:20,030
<i>SUBJECT: WAS THAT YOU?</i>

219
00:12:20,114 --> 00:12:24,201
<i>[Max]</i> Dear Babu. I'm not sure
if it was you I saw earlier.

220
00:12:26,620 --> 00:12:28,205
<i>But if it was really you,</i>

221
00:12:28,998 --> 00:12:31,167
<i>I don't think I would've talked to you.</i>

222
00:12:31,959 --> 00:12:34,295
<i>To this day, I still don't understand</i>

223
00:12:34,378 --> 00:12:36,797
<i>and I'm still hurt by what you did.</i>

224
00:12:37,757 --> 00:12:40,760
<i>No matter how many times my friends say</i>

225
00:12:40,843 --> 00:12:42,470
<i>that Enrile likes me,</i>

226
00:12:43,304 --> 00:12:45,931
<i>that he sees me as more than a friend,</i>

227
00:12:46,640 --> 00:12:48,225
<i>I can't bring myself to believe it.</i>

228
00:12:49,059 --> 00:12:51,270
<i>Because I trusted you before,</i>

229
00:12:52,021 --> 00:12:54,023
<i>and yet you failed me.</i>

230
00:12:55,566 --> 00:12:59,403
<i>Up to now, I still ask myself,</i>

231
00:13:01,363 --> 00:13:02,823
<i>"Was any of that real?"</i>

232
00:13:04,033 --> 00:13:08,579
<i>Were you honest when you made me</i>
<i>feel like I mattered to you?</i>

233
00:13:10,122 --> 00:13:14,251
<i>Or was I just imagining that</i>
<i>you loved me because I loved you?</i>

234
00:13:19,840 --> 00:13:20,883
<i>[knocking on door]</i>

235
00:13:22,301 --> 00:13:24,053
<i>Hi. Can I come in?</i>

236
00:13:24,136 --> 00:13:26,305
<i>Oh, sure.</i>

237
00:13:34,522 --> 00:13:36,023
<i>Why are you still up?</i>

238
00:13:36,690 --> 00:13:37,817
<i>Did you just get in?</i>

239
00:13:37,900 --> 00:13:38,943
<i>Yes, Dad.</i>

240
00:13:39,944 --> 00:13:42,112
<i>I had a late shift at The Barb.</i>

241
00:13:42,696 --> 00:13:43,823
<i>Have you eaten?</i>

242
00:13:43,906 --> 00:13:46,492
<i>Yeah. I had a working dinner.</i>

243
00:13:48,953 --> 00:13:51,580
<i>Listen, I won't stop you from working.</i>

244
00:13:51,664 --> 00:13:54,416
<i>I just want you to know</i>

245
00:13:55,835 --> 00:13:58,003
<i>I'm worried whenever you come home late.</i>

246
00:13:58,796 --> 00:14:02,383
<i>Criminals are more likely</i>
<i>to strike in the dark.</i>

247
00:14:02,967 --> 00:14:05,219
<i>Don't worry about me, Dad.</i>

248
00:14:05,845 --> 00:14:08,472
<i>I know how to defend myself</i>
<i>against those criminals.</i>

249
00:14:08,556 --> 00:14:10,349
<i>I was a "gangster" in Mindoro!</i>

250
00:14:11,183 --> 00:14:13,394
<i>[chuckles] Just like your mom.</i>

251
00:14:14,228 --> 00:14:15,688
<i>She was a gangster too.</i>

252
00:14:15,771 --> 00:14:18,649
<i>Do you know how we met in Mindoro?</i>

253
00:14:19,525 --> 00:14:20,609
<i>No.</i>

254
00:14:21,694 --> 00:14:23,070
<i>I was in the market.</i>

255
00:14:25,322 --> 00:14:27,199
<i>She was gonna steal my wallet.</i>

256
00:14:27,992 --> 00:14:29,243
<i>But I caught her.</i>

257
00:14:29,869 --> 00:14:31,495
<i>I didn't tell the police</i>

258
00:14:31,579 --> 00:14:34,623
<i>because she told me</i>
<i>that her brother was sick.</i>

259
00:14:35,958 --> 00:14:37,084
<i>You mean Uncle Boyet?</i>

260
00:14:37,167 --> 00:14:38,168
<i>Yeah.</i>

261
00:14:38,752 --> 00:14:41,672
<i>-But he's so healthy!</i>
<i>-[chuckles] That's right.</i>

262
00:14:41,755 --> 00:14:43,465
<i>It turned out to be an alibi!</i>

263
00:14:44,174 --> 00:14:45,551
<i>I actually asked her,</i>

264
00:14:45,634 --> 00:14:47,386
<i>"Why do you have to steal?"</i>

265
00:14:49,513 --> 00:14:51,348
<i>She said it was okay.</i>

266
00:14:51,432 --> 00:14:53,434
<i>It's okay to steal from the rich.</i>

267
00:14:53,517 --> 00:14:55,769
<i>I should treat it as charity work.</i>

268
00:14:57,938 --> 00:15:00,232
<i>No wonder she didn't tell me.</i>

269
00:15:03,402 --> 00:15:06,405
<i>[sighs] I miss Mama.</i>

270
00:15:10,367 --> 00:15:11,452
<i>Yeah.</i>

271
00:15:12,953 --> 00:15:15,456
<i>I'm sorry I wasn't there</i>
<i>when you were younger.</i>

272
00:15:16,749 --> 00:15:19,668
<i>If only your mom had told me…</i>

273
00:15:20,502 --> 00:15:24,632
<i>Maybe things would have been different.</i>

274
00:15:27,551 --> 00:15:30,054
<i>Maybe she wouldn't have died</i>
<i>in a tsunami in Japan.</i>

275
00:15:32,890 --> 00:15:35,684
<i>Maybe I wouldn't be this tough.</i>

276
00:15:36,936 --> 00:15:38,228
<i>It's okay, Dad.</i>

277
00:15:38,854 --> 00:15:41,190
<i>Everything turned out well in the end.</i>

278
00:15:43,609 --> 00:15:46,153
<i>If things were different, maybe</i>
<i>you wouldn't be this happy</i>

279
00:15:46,236 --> 00:15:47,696
<i>together with Aunt Macy,</i>

280
00:15:48,781 --> 00:15:51,075
<i>Elle, and Maxrill.</i>

281
00:15:51,867 --> 00:15:53,535
<i>Yeah. Yeah…</i>

282
00:15:54,662 --> 00:15:56,080
<i>But I want to assure you,</i>

283
00:15:56,580 --> 00:15:58,374
<i>if only your mom told me</i>

284
00:15:59,625 --> 00:16:01,043
<i>that she was pregnant with you,</i>

285
00:16:02,586 --> 00:16:04,713
<i>I would have wanted you.</i>

286
00:16:05,756 --> 00:16:08,717
<i>I would have taken care of you right away.</i>

287
00:16:09,551 --> 00:16:11,512
<i>I would have been proud of you.</i>

288
00:16:12,012 --> 00:16:13,639
<i>I wouldn't have hidden you.</i>

289
00:16:13,722 --> 00:16:15,516
<i>I would never deny you.</i>

290
00:16:16,308 --> 00:16:20,896
<i>I will not make you doubt or question</i>

291
00:16:21,689 --> 00:16:23,107
<i>if I love you.</i>

292
00:16:25,025 --> 00:16:26,360
<i>And I want you to know,</i>

293
00:16:27,444 --> 00:16:29,405
<i>no matter what other people say,</i>

294
00:16:32,825 --> 00:16:34,034
<i>I loved your mom.</i>

295
00:16:37,830 --> 00:16:38,914
<i>I really did.</i>

296
00:16:39,748 --> 00:16:43,419
<i>[emotional music playing]</i>

297
00:17:01,562 --> 00:17:04,606
<i>Mom, I need you to sign this--</i>

298
00:17:06,316 --> 00:17:07,526
<i>[Macy sniffles]</i>

299
00:17:07,609 --> 00:17:09,069
<i>Are you okay, Mom?</i>

300
00:17:09,153 --> 00:17:10,571
<i>Yeah, I am.</i>

301
00:17:11,572 --> 00:17:13,240
<i>You need something, baby?</i>

302
00:17:13,323 --> 00:17:15,034
<i>I need to hug my mom.</i>

303
00:17:17,369 --> 00:17:18,662
<i>I love you, Mom.</i>

304
00:17:19,288 --> 00:17:20,748
<i>I love you, baby.</i>

305
00:17:25,419 --> 00:17:27,379
<i>[both sobbing]</i>

306
00:17:39,933 --> 00:17:43,771
<i>HOW SWEET!</i>

307
00:17:43,854 --> 00:17:46,565
<i>[emotional music continues]</i>

308
00:18:32,236 --> 00:18:37,616
<i>LOVE HOW IT WAS DONE! SO SWEET.</i>

309
00:18:43,747 --> 00:18:46,959
<i>[hand slaps table]</i>
<i>The nerve of that squammy girl!</i>

310
00:18:47,042 --> 00:18:49,128
<i>Who does she think she is?</i>

311
00:18:49,211 --> 00:18:51,088
<i>Always trying to get Deib's attention!</i>

312
00:18:51,672 --> 00:18:53,590
<i>She's not even pretty!</i>

313
00:18:53,674 --> 00:18:55,342
<i>Has she even looked at the mirror?</i>

314
00:18:55,425 --> 00:18:57,719
<i>An entire car can fit up in her nose!</i>

315
00:18:58,470 --> 00:19:01,640
<i>If only Kim were here,</i>

316
00:19:01,723 --> 00:19:06,770
<i>she wouldn't even let Deib</i>
<i>within ten feet of Max. Right?</i>

317
00:19:07,563 --> 00:19:10,357
<i>Well, why don't we call Kim</i>

318
00:19:10,440 --> 00:19:12,943
<i>and ask her to come back to Benison?</i>

319
00:19:13,694 --> 00:19:17,698
<i>Khloe, how are we friends?</i>
<i>You're so stupid!</i>

320
00:19:18,657 --> 00:19:20,951
<i>Aimee, that was mean.</i>

321
00:19:21,034 --> 00:19:22,744
<i>What? I was just being honest.</i>

322
00:19:22,828 --> 00:19:25,122
<i>Imagine. If Kim comes back,</i>

323
00:19:25,205 --> 00:19:28,208
<i>then we wouldn't be</i>
<i>the coolest girls in Benison anymore.</i>

324
00:19:28,292 --> 00:19:30,669
<i>Plus, I wouldn't have a chance with Deib.</i>

325
00:19:32,379 --> 00:19:36,884
<i>What we need to do</i>
<i>is get Max out of Benison.</i>

326
00:19:36,967 --> 00:19:38,552
<i>Do you want me to scare her</i>

327
00:19:39,344 --> 00:19:41,555
<i>so she'll leave Benison?</i>

328
00:19:42,514 --> 00:19:45,184
<i>Just say the word, and I'll do it.</i>

329
00:19:52,232 --> 00:19:54,276
<i>I miss you guys!</i>

330
00:19:55,444 --> 00:19:57,487
<i>Did you mean all of us or just Master Lee?</i>

331
00:19:58,155 --> 00:20:00,324
<i>Hey, come on.</i>

332
00:20:00,949 --> 00:20:02,284
<i>I miss hanging out with you guys.</i>

333
00:20:02,367 --> 00:20:05,829
<i>Did you mean all of us or just Michiko?</i>

334
00:20:05,913 --> 00:20:06,830
<i>Stop it, guys.</i>

335
00:20:06,914 --> 00:20:09,166
<i>[girls squealing, giggling]</i>

336
00:20:10,334 --> 00:20:11,293
<i>[slams]</i>

337
00:20:14,630 --> 00:20:15,756
<i>[Lee] Get your order, boys.</i>

338
00:20:16,590 --> 00:20:18,342
<i>-What you want, dude?</i>
<i>-Wait a minute.</i>

339
00:20:20,928 --> 00:20:21,803
<i>[woman] Hello?</i>

340
00:20:25,807 --> 00:20:27,476
<i>[Tob] Who is Deib talking to?</i>

341
00:20:27,559 --> 00:20:29,228
<i>[Lee] Definitely not my cousin.</i>

342
00:20:29,311 --> 00:20:32,022
<i>[Lorde] Oh my goodness.</i>
<i>What if it's Queen Kim?</i>

343
00:20:32,105 --> 00:20:33,398
<i>[Tob] I don't think so, Lorde.</i>

344
00:20:38,445 --> 00:20:39,529
<i>Guys.</i>

345
00:20:41,490 --> 00:20:45,035
<i>When is this cold war between</i>
<i>Max and Deib gonna end?</i>

346
00:20:45,118 --> 00:20:49,248
<i>Maybe we need to find a way</i>
<i>to make them talk again.</i>

347
00:20:49,331 --> 00:20:52,125
<i>How? Will they work on another project?</i>

348
00:20:52,751 --> 00:20:54,002
<i>[Lee] Or…</i>

349
00:20:54,086 --> 00:20:55,921
<i>let's make them our project.</i>

350
00:20:57,547 --> 00:21:00,008
<i>That's it.</i>

351
00:21:01,802 --> 00:21:03,679
<i>[Lee narrates text]</i>

352
00:21:03,762 --> 00:21:06,223
<i>[Lorde] </i>Project TagSen Together Again.

353
00:21:06,306 --> 00:21:09,101
<i>There. I changed the name</i>
<i>to make it clear.</i>

354
00:21:09,184 --> 00:21:12,396
<i>[Naih] </i>Guys, how do we end their FQ?

355
00:21:12,980 --> 00:21:15,983
<i>-[Migz]</i> "FQ"?
<i>-[Naih]</i> Friendship quarrel.

356
00:21:16,066 --> 00:21:19,987
<i>[Michiko] </i>They said they're not friends,
which means it's not an FQ.

357
00:21:20,070 --> 00:21:21,613
<i>[Lorde] </i>EQ, then.

358
00:21:21,697 --> 00:21:23,240
<i>[Tob] </i>Emotional quotient?

359
00:21:23,323 --> 00:21:26,994
<i>[Lorde] </i>Too smart, Master!
I meant "Enemies Quarrel."

360
00:21:27,077 --> 00:21:28,287
<i>[Migz] </i>You're so corny, Lorde!

361
00:21:29,079 --> 00:21:31,039
<i>[Ysay] </i>But I don't think they're enemies.

362
00:21:31,123 --> 00:21:32,582
<i>It's just a misunderstanding.</i>

363
00:21:33,292 --> 00:21:36,253
<i>[Migz] </i>Guys, we need to
get them talking again.

364
00:21:36,336 --> 00:21:38,171
<i>But we can't be too obvious about it.</i>

365
00:21:38,255 --> 00:21:40,549
<i>[Lee] </i>This is the plan. After practice,

366
00:21:40,632 --> 00:21:42,718
<i>Tob and I will be in the auditorium,</i>

367
00:21:42,801 --> 00:21:45,012
<i>pretending like I'm planning</i>
<i>a date for Max.</i>

368
00:21:45,095 --> 00:21:46,930
<i>[Tob]</i> I like where you're going with this.

369
00:21:47,014 --> 00:21:48,974
<i>[Naih] </i>You're just pretending, right, Lee?

370
00:21:49,057 --> 00:21:50,892
<i>[Lee] </i>We're just going
to give him a little push

371
00:21:50,976 --> 00:21:53,895
<i>to make the first move to talk to Max.</i>

372
00:21:53,979 --> 00:21:55,731
<i>[Tob] </i>Michiko, you and
the rest of the girls

373
00:21:55,814 --> 00:21:58,650
<i>have to convince Max</i>
<i>not to shut down Deib.</i>

374
00:21:59,401 --> 00:22:05,115
<i>[Michiko] </i>Okay. I just hope Max
doesn't see through our plan.

375
00:22:05,198 --> 00:22:07,326
<i>[Tob] </i>Don't worry about it.
We can do this.

376
00:22:07,409 --> 00:22:08,910
<i>[Ysay] </i>Let's do this, guys!

377
00:22:09,911 --> 00:22:11,705
<i>[Lorde] </i>Sorry. Phone died.

378
00:22:11,788 --> 00:22:15,417
<i>Masters, what's my role? Masters?</i>

379
00:22:16,168 --> 00:22:17,544
<i>Hello?</i>

380
00:22:17,627 --> 00:22:19,296
<i>[inaudible chatter]</i>

381
00:22:19,379 --> 00:22:20,756
<i>What are we doing here?</i>

382
00:22:20,839 --> 00:22:23,633
<i>-Nothing. We're just gonna chill.</i>
<i>-What are you up to?</i>

383
00:22:26,053 --> 00:22:27,679
<i>[Tob] </i>Deib is here. Game.

384
00:22:31,099 --> 00:22:34,770
<i>Dude, has Max agreed to go out</i>
<i>on a date with you?</i>

385
00:22:35,479 --> 00:22:37,606
<i>[Lee] Yeah. I already asked her earlier.</i>

386
00:22:37,689 --> 00:22:40,233
<i>She told me to pick her up at The Barb.</i>

387
00:22:40,817 --> 00:22:42,527
<i>[Tob] </i>Deib knows.

388
00:22:42,611 --> 00:22:44,279
<i>Did I hear that right?</i>

389
00:22:45,530 --> 00:22:47,949
<i>You asked Max out on a date?</i>

390
00:22:48,867 --> 00:22:49,743
<i>Yeah.</i>

391
00:22:51,536 --> 00:22:53,121
<i>I don't see any problem with that.</i>

392
00:22:53,205 --> 00:22:56,083
<i>[Lee] Besides, you're not into her right?</i>

393
00:22:57,167 --> 00:22:58,835
<i>[Tob] Yeah. I agree with him.</i>

394
00:22:59,836 --> 00:23:02,005
<i>Yeah. Of course.</i>

395
00:23:02,547 --> 00:23:05,175
<i>[Tob] </i>Deib knows. I think
he's gonna message Max now.

396
00:23:05,967 --> 00:23:10,555
<i>MEET ME AT THE LOCKER AREA AFTER</i>
<i>MY PRACTICE. WE NEED TO TALK.</i>

397
00:23:10,639 --> 00:23:13,642
<i>[inaudible whispering]</i>

398
00:23:15,644 --> 00:23:19,689
<i>[Deib]</i> Meet me at the locker area
after my practice. We need to talk.

399
00:23:19,773 --> 00:23:22,234
<i>The nerve of this Enrile!</i>

400
00:23:22,317 --> 00:23:24,486
<i>He acts like he's my boss.</i>

401
00:23:25,320 --> 00:23:27,864
<i>[Michiko] </i>Tell Deib to be nicer.

402
00:23:27,948 --> 00:23:30,200
<i>I suggest you should be nice to Max.</i>

403
00:23:30,909 --> 00:23:31,993
<i>Right!</i>

404
00:23:32,077 --> 00:23:35,205
<i>[Lee] I will always say "please" to her.</i>

405
00:23:46,633 --> 00:23:48,593
<i>-[phone vibrates]</i>
<i>-[Deib] </i>Please?

406
00:23:49,344 --> 00:23:53,056
<i>Ha! So, you have some manners!</i>

407
00:23:54,015 --> 00:23:57,269
<i>WHAT ARE WE TALKING ABOUT?</i>

408
00:23:57,352 --> 00:24:00,772
<i>TELL HIM TO BE HONEST.</i>

409
00:24:00,856 --> 00:24:03,233
<i>[Max] </i>What are we talking about?

410
00:24:03,316 --> 00:24:05,694
<i>[Michiko] </i>Tell him to be honest.

411
00:24:05,777 --> 00:24:07,571
<i>I think you should tell her the truth.</i>

412
00:24:09,364 --> 00:24:14,327
<i>Right. I should be </i>honest
<i>about my feelings.</i>

413
00:24:20,500 --> 00:24:24,045
<i>Our friends are having a hard time</i>
<i>with us constantly arguing.</i>

414
00:24:24,880 --> 00:24:25,881
<i>What?</i>

415
00:24:26,756 --> 00:24:30,093
<i>So it's my fault now?</i>
<i>He's the one with the problem.</i>

416
00:24:32,095 --> 00:24:33,805
<i>Wait, are we stressing you out?</i>

417
00:24:33,889 --> 00:24:36,641
<i>Of course not! We're actually</i>
<i>enjoying your romance!</i>

418
00:24:36,725 --> 00:24:38,226
<i>Max, please!</i>

419
00:24:38,310 --> 00:24:41,146
<i>Your war with Deib is wrecking</i>
<i>my romantic plans with Lee.</i>

420
00:24:41,229 --> 00:24:42,731
<i>And as you know,</i>

421
00:24:42,814 --> 00:24:45,609
<i>my goal in life is to be friends</i>
<i>with all the Benisonians.</i>

422
00:24:45,692 --> 00:24:46,860
<i>-[Michiko] Yes!</i>
<i>-[Migz] True!</i>

423
00:24:46,943 --> 00:24:49,863
<i>-The same with Tob and me.</i>
<i>-Oh! You too, huh?</i>

424
00:24:49,946 --> 00:24:52,991
<i>-Don't we need to go somewhere?</i>
<i>-That's right.</i>

425
00:24:53,074 --> 00:24:54,701
<i>-Girl, you can do this.</i>
<i>-Oh right!</i>

426
00:24:54,784 --> 00:24:56,703
<i>Don't leave me with that guy!</i>
<i>Where are you going?</i>

427
00:24:56,786 --> 00:24:58,788
<i>[Migz] Come on.</i>
<i>You can handle him! You can do this!</i>

428
00:24:58,872 --> 00:25:00,707
<i>-You're a big girl. You know what to do!</i>
<i>-Wait.</i>

429
00:25:00,790 --> 00:25:02,959
<i>-[Migz] Gotta go!</i>
<i>-Hey, guys! Stay!</i>

430
00:25:03,043 --> 00:25:04,794
<i>-[Naih] Bye, Max!</i>
<i>-[Ysay] Bye.</i>

431
00:25:04,878 --> 00:25:05,837
<i>Bye, bye.</i>

432
00:25:09,674 --> 00:25:11,384
<i>-[phone vibrates]</i>
<i>-[Max]</i> K.

433
00:25:12,302 --> 00:25:13,136
<i>"K"? That's it?</i>

434
00:25:21,269 --> 00:25:23,230
<i>[Lorde] Master, where are you going?</i>

435
00:25:25,357 --> 00:25:27,651
<i>It worked! Yes!</i>

436
00:25:39,412 --> 00:25:41,998
<i>[unsettling music playing]</i>

437
00:25:52,634 --> 00:25:54,678
<i>[Max] </i>I'm on my way to the locker area.

438
00:26:03,228 --> 00:26:06,064
<i>[sinister music playing]</i>

439
00:26:25,250 --> 00:26:26,543
<i>[thuds]</i>

440
00:26:35,427 --> 00:26:36,261
<i>Max?</i>

441
00:26:37,929 --> 00:26:38,763
<i>Max!</i>

442
00:26:40,515 --> 00:26:42,809
<i>Max, Max.</i>

443
00:26:46,438 --> 00:26:48,231
<i>What happened to you?</i>

444
00:26:51,318 --> 00:26:52,277
<i>[Deib] Max!</i>

445
00:26:52,360 --> 00:26:53,528
<i>Max!</i>

446
00:26:53,612 --> 00:26:54,571
<i>Max!</i>

447
00:26:55,238 --> 00:26:56,281
<i>Max, wake up.</i>

448
00:27:13,673 --> 00:27:16,343
<i>[doctor] …this is a very sensitive matter.</i>

449
00:27:16,426 --> 00:27:19,220
<i>[conversation continues indistinctly]</i>

450
00:27:19,304 --> 00:27:20,889
<i>-We're so worried.</i>
<i>-Max.</i>

451
00:27:20,972 --> 00:27:23,391
<i>-Kids. Kids. Kids.</i>
<i>-Give her some space, please.</i>

452
00:27:23,975 --> 00:27:25,143
<i>What happened?</i>

453
00:27:26,561 --> 00:27:27,812
<i>Where am I?</i>

454
00:27:28,563 --> 00:27:29,939
<i>You lost consciousness.</i>

455
00:27:30,023 --> 00:27:34,027
<i>Fortunately, your friend found you</i>
<i>and brought you here to the hospital.</i>

456
00:27:35,028 --> 00:27:36,529
<i>Which friend?</i>

457
00:27:36,613 --> 00:27:38,907
<i>[headmaster] Mr. Enrile brought you here.</i>

458
00:27:39,491 --> 00:27:42,410
<i>Max! Are you feeling okay? How are you?</i>

459
00:27:42,994 --> 00:27:45,205
<i>-Are you okay?</i>
<i>-[Maxim] I'm her father.</i>

460
00:27:45,288 --> 00:27:46,623
<i>[doctor] I'm the physician.</i>

461
00:27:46,706 --> 00:27:47,707
<i>-Is that…?</i>
<i>-Oh my gosh.</i>

462
00:27:47,791 --> 00:27:50,460
<i>Based on the story of Deib here,</i>

463
00:27:50,543 --> 00:27:52,879
<i>he found your daughter unconscious.</i>

464
00:27:53,505 --> 00:27:56,341
<i>[doctor] But based on</i>
<i>our initial findings,</i>

465
00:27:56,424 --> 00:27:58,802
<i>she suffered a head trauma</i>.

466
00:28:00,261 --> 00:28:03,390
<i>Max, did anyone see your assailant?</i>

467
00:28:06,476 --> 00:28:09,145
<i>[doctor] Anyway, we will still</i>
<i>be running some tests on her</i>

468
00:28:09,229 --> 00:28:12,315
<i>for us to determine</i>
<i>the extent of the injury.</i>

469
00:28:13,358 --> 00:28:15,860
<i>-Thank you, Doc. Please go ahead.</i>
<i>-Excuse me.</i>

470
00:28:15,944 --> 00:28:18,697
<i>[Maxim] Elle, please go outside</i>
<i>with your schoolmates.</i>

471
00:28:18,780 --> 00:28:21,574
<i>I have to discuss some matters</i>
<i>with the headmaster.</i>

472
00:28:22,325 --> 00:28:25,245
<i>-[headmaster] All right. Let's go guys.</i>
<i>-[Macy] Kids, let's go.</i>

473
00:28:28,998 --> 00:28:31,334
<i>[Maxim] Excuse me. [clears throat]</i>

474
00:28:37,132 --> 00:28:38,967
<i>You're Deib Enrile, correct?</i>

475
00:28:39,634 --> 00:28:40,927
<i>Yes.</i>

476
00:28:41,010 --> 00:28:44,097
<i>Well, thank you for bringing</i>
<i>my daughter here.</i>

477
00:28:45,974 --> 00:28:48,101
<i>I've heard stories about you.</i>

478
00:28:50,645 --> 00:28:53,440
<i>I don't want any more trouble for Max.</i>

479
00:28:53,523 --> 00:28:57,152
<i>So, please, keep your distance from her.</i>

480
00:28:57,235 --> 00:28:59,612
<i>[somber music playing]</i>

481
00:29:07,704 --> 00:29:09,414
<i>You don't remember anything?</i>

482
00:29:10,582 --> 00:29:11,624
<i>[Naih] Oh my God!</i>

483
00:29:11,708 --> 00:29:16,588
<i>So if Elle and Max have the same dad,</i>
<i>that means they're sisters?</i>

484
00:29:16,671 --> 00:29:19,132
<i>-[Naih] Oh my God!</i>
<i>-[Ysay] Like Cinderella.</i>

485
00:29:19,215 --> 00:29:21,885
<i>That's right!</i>
<i>And Elle is the evil stepsister.</i>

486
00:29:21,968 --> 00:29:23,136
<i>Hey, that's too much!</i>

487
00:29:23,219 --> 00:29:24,429
<i>I can hear you, guys.</i>

488
00:29:24,512 --> 00:29:26,723
<i>[Elle] And if you're going</i>
<i>to talk about our family,</i>

489
00:29:26,806 --> 00:29:29,225
<i>the least you can do</i>
<i>is be subtle about it.</i>

490
00:29:32,520 --> 00:29:33,605
<i>[Naih laughs]</i>

491
00:29:33,688 --> 00:29:36,274
<i>But how come Max never told us?</i>

492
00:29:36,357 --> 00:29:37,192
<i>True.</i>

493
00:29:38,651 --> 00:29:42,405
<i>She just didn't know how to tell you guys.</i>

494
00:29:42,489 --> 00:29:44,032
<i>[all] You know about it?</i>

495
00:29:44,115 --> 00:29:45,450
<i>How?</i>

496
00:29:46,868 --> 00:29:48,703
<i>[Deib] </i>Trying to discover
who we really are.

497
00:29:49,537 --> 00:29:51,831
<i>Trying to be accepted</i>
<i>for who we really are.</i>

498
00:29:51,915 --> 00:29:54,626
<i>And trying to be loved</i>
<i>for who we really are.</i>

499
00:29:56,836 --> 00:29:58,213
<i>That okay with you?</i>

500
00:29:58,296 --> 00:30:01,216
<i>Not bad. Is this based on</i>
<i>your own personal experience?</i>

501
00:30:02,383 --> 00:30:04,385
<i>But don't we all feel that way?</i>

502
00:30:05,720 --> 00:30:07,472
<i>[phone vibrating]</i>

503
00:30:11,643 --> 00:30:13,645
<i>-[Maxim] </i>Hello, Max?
<i>-Hello, Dad?</i>

504
00:30:13,728 --> 00:30:15,271
<i>Where are you? It's late.</i>

505
00:30:15,355 --> 00:30:18,691
<i>I'm just at my classmate's house.</i>
<i>We're finishing a project.</i>

506
00:30:18,775 --> 00:30:21,653
<i>-Do you want the driver to pick you up?</i>
-No need. I'll go home on my own.

507
00:30:21,736 --> 00:30:23,196
<i>Okay. Take care.</i>

508
00:30:23,279 --> 00:30:24,447
<i>I will. Bye.</i>

509
00:30:28,451 --> 00:30:29,994
<i>You asked about my family.</i>

510
00:30:30,078 --> 00:30:31,538
<i>Can I ask about yours?</i>

511
00:30:33,790 --> 00:30:35,291
<i>Are you close to your dad?</i>

512
00:30:38,253 --> 00:30:39,212
<i>No.</i>

513
00:30:40,672 --> 00:30:43,716
<i>Actually, I just met him recently.</i>

514
00:30:43,800 --> 00:30:46,427
<i>He and my mom separated years ago.</i>

515
00:30:48,137 --> 00:30:49,097
<i>But it's fine.</i>

516
00:30:50,265 --> 00:30:52,976
<i>Growing up, I wasn't lacking in love.</i>

517
00:30:54,477 --> 00:30:55,812
<i>When did they separate?</i>

518
00:30:56,980 --> 00:30:58,648
<i>Actually, they never got married.</i>

519
00:30:59,691 --> 00:31:03,152
<i>It was just a whirlwind romance</i>
<i>when my dad got assigned to Mindoro.</i>

520
00:31:04,070 --> 00:31:07,156
<i>And my dad's Chinese family</i>
<i>disliked my mom.</i>

521
00:31:07,657 --> 00:31:10,368
<i>She was poor, unrefined,</i>
<i>a bit of a gangster.</i>

522
00:31:10,451 --> 00:31:11,911
<i>And worse, not Chinese.</i>

523
00:31:12,787 --> 00:31:15,665
<i>She wasn't worthy of the heir</i>
<i>of Luna Industries.</i>

524
00:31:19,252 --> 00:31:20,837
<i>Luna Industries?</i>

525
00:31:21,713 --> 00:31:23,506
<i>I think there's a Luna in school…</i>

526
00:31:23,590 --> 00:31:24,424
<i>Elle.</i>

527
00:31:25,717 --> 00:31:27,010
<i>She's my half-sister.</i>

528
00:31:28,011 --> 00:31:29,554
<i>But don't tell anyone.</i>

529
00:31:29,637 --> 00:31:33,474
<i>Elle would hate it</i>
<i>if the entire school knew.</i>

530
00:31:34,392 --> 00:31:36,561
<i>Okay. But how about you?</i>

531
00:31:37,437 --> 00:31:40,523
<i>You okay with our classmates</i>
<i>knowing about this?</i>

532
00:31:42,483 --> 00:31:43,610
<i>It's okay with me.</i>

533
00:31:44,444 --> 00:31:46,404
<i>I'm not ashamed of who I am.</i>

534
00:31:46,988 --> 00:31:49,240
<i>But I get where Elle is coming from.</i>

535
00:31:49,324 --> 00:31:51,743
<i>Even if she's annoying,</i>
<i>I really do understand.</i>

536
00:31:51,826 --> 00:31:54,537
<i>She just wants to keep her family whole.</i>

537
00:31:55,830 --> 00:31:56,998
<i>I'm sure you get that.</i>

538
00:31:59,584 --> 00:32:00,793
<i>More than you know.</i>

539
00:32:03,296 --> 00:32:04,172
<i>Hmm.</i>

540
00:32:05,840 --> 00:32:06,799
<i>What's that?</i>

541
00:32:06,883 --> 00:32:08,468
<i>Let's do a pinky promise.</i>

542
00:32:09,510 --> 00:32:12,138
<i>Promise you won't tell</i>
<i>the others in school about this.</i>

543
00:32:12,931 --> 00:32:14,432
<i>Don't you trust me?</i>

544
00:32:15,016 --> 00:32:18,686
<i>When I was in third grade,</i>
<i>I had an award: Most Trustworthy.</i>

545
00:32:23,816 --> 00:32:25,234
<i>I'm serious.</i>

546
00:32:25,318 --> 00:32:28,988
<i>Even if Elle is a brat,</i>
<i>she's still my sister.</i>

547
00:32:30,365 --> 00:32:31,950
<i>Your secret is safe with me.</i>

548
00:32:33,743 --> 00:32:35,495
<i>Your secret is safe with me too.</i>

549
00:32:41,042 --> 00:32:43,753
<i>Guys, family is important to Max and Elle.</i>

550
00:32:43,836 --> 00:32:46,047
<i>So, let's just</i>
<i>respect their privacy. Okay?</i>

551
00:32:46,714 --> 00:32:47,674
<i>[Tob] Got it, dude!</i>

552
00:32:47,757 --> 00:32:49,634
<i>-[Tob chuckles]</i>
<i>-[Lorde clears throat]</i>

553
00:32:49,717 --> 00:32:50,760
<i>Master.</i>

554
00:32:50,843 --> 00:32:51,719
<i>What?</i>

555
00:32:51,803 --> 00:32:55,598
<i>I didn't know you and Max</i>
<i>were that close already.</i>

556
00:32:56,182 --> 00:32:59,727
<i>But how's that?</i>
<i>You failed her dad's boyfriend test.</i>

557
00:32:59,811 --> 00:33:02,522
<i>[all laughing]</i>

558
00:33:02,605 --> 00:33:03,523
<i>[Tob] Dude.</i>

559
00:33:04,399 --> 00:33:06,192
<i>Why? I'm not courting her.</i>

560
00:33:06,275 --> 00:33:08,111
<i>Really now?</i>

561
00:33:08,194 --> 00:33:09,153
<i>[headmaster] Guys.</i>

562
00:33:10,321 --> 00:33:14,283
<i>Max is back in her room with her parents,</i>
<i>so there's not much we can do, right?</i>

563
00:33:14,367 --> 00:33:16,119
<i>I suggest we go rest.</i>
<i>It's been a long day.</i>

564
00:33:16,202 --> 00:33:17,787
<i>-Yeah?</i>
<i>-[Migz] Yes, Sir.</i>

565
00:33:20,248 --> 00:33:21,124
<i>[headmaster] See you!</i>

566
00:33:21,207 --> 00:33:22,500
<i>-Bye, sir.</i>
<i>-[Ysay] Thank you.</i>

567
00:33:22,583 --> 00:33:26,462
<i>-[headmaster] Yes, yes. Behave!</i>
<i>-Michiko, you want me to bring you home?</i>

568
00:33:27,964 --> 00:33:28,965
<i>[squeals]</i>

569
00:33:32,051 --> 00:33:35,555
<i>Are you sure? My house is out of the way.</i>

570
00:33:35,638 --> 00:33:36,723
<i>Don't worry about it.</i>

571
00:33:37,849 --> 00:33:39,100
<i>Michiko. Go!</i>

572
00:33:40,643 --> 00:33:41,936
<i>Okay.</i>

573
00:33:44,230 --> 00:33:45,898
<i>[Tob] All right. Good night to you, bro.</i>

574
00:33:45,982 --> 00:33:48,067
<i>[Migz speaking indistinctly]</i>

575
00:33:48,151 --> 00:33:49,235
<i>Okay. Take care.</i>

576
00:33:50,028 --> 00:33:51,029
<i>-Bye!</i>
<i>-Bye!</i>

577
00:33:52,321 --> 00:33:55,616
<i>Girls, it's already late.</i>
<i>Do you need a ride home?</i>

578
00:33:55,700 --> 00:33:57,076
<i>-Yes please!</i>
<i>-I do!</i>

579
00:33:58,119 --> 00:34:00,288
<i>All right. I'll bring you two home.</i>

580
00:34:03,916 --> 00:34:05,251
<i>I'll just ride with Migz.</i>

581
00:34:05,918 --> 00:34:08,212
<i>-[Ysay] My house is closer to his place.</i>
<i>-You sure?</i>

582
00:34:08,921 --> 00:34:11,257
<i>Master!</i>
<i>I still get to sit in front, right?</i>

583
00:34:12,842 --> 00:34:15,344
<i>Migz, can Lorde ride with you instead?</i>

584
00:34:15,428 --> 00:34:17,055
<i>-Why?</i>
<i>-Thanks, man. Let's go.</i>

585
00:34:17,805 --> 00:34:19,348
<i>Bye!</i>

586
00:34:19,432 --> 00:34:25,146
<i>I, the Lorde be with you,</i>
<i>President Migz and Madam Ysay.</i>

587
00:34:27,315 --> 00:34:28,983
<i>Deib, are you coming with us?</i>

588
00:34:29,567 --> 00:34:32,236
<i>Go ahead. I'm gonna visit my brother.</i>

589
00:34:36,657 --> 00:34:38,367
<i>Keep an eye on Max.</i>

590
00:34:39,160 --> 00:34:40,328
<i>Hey, wait for me.</i>

591
00:34:42,163 --> 00:34:46,209
<i>Her results came back.</i>
<i>There's no traumatic injury to her brain.</i>

592
00:34:46,292 --> 00:34:49,796
<i>But she may still experience mild nausea.</i>

593
00:34:49,879 --> 00:34:54,967
<i>It would be best if Max</i>
<i>stays the night for observation.</i>

594
00:34:55,635 --> 00:34:57,261
<i>Okay. Thank you, Doc.</i>

595
00:34:57,762 --> 00:34:59,013
<i>Thank you.</i>

596
00:35:03,518 --> 00:35:04,811
<i>[Macy] Let me do it, Max.</i>

597
00:35:06,312 --> 00:35:07,563
<i>How are you feeling, Max?</i>

598
00:35:08,981 --> 00:35:10,733
<i>I'm feeling better now.</i>

599
00:35:11,400 --> 00:35:13,945
<i>Let us know if you need anything, okay?</i>

600
00:35:14,028 --> 00:35:15,196
<i>Drink this.</i>

601
00:35:15,780 --> 00:35:19,367
<i>[Maxim sighs deeply] I can't believe</i>
<i>this could happen in Benison.</i>

602
00:35:20,535 --> 00:35:23,621
<i>I'm setting a meeting with the school</i>
<i>board to discuss the investigation.</i>

603
00:35:25,039 --> 00:35:28,376
<i>Max, do you know someone</i>
<i>that might do this to you?</i>

604
00:35:28,459 --> 00:35:31,045
<i>Dad, don't bombard Max with questions.</i>

605
00:35:31,129 --> 00:35:32,797
<i>[Elle] She might get a headache.</i>

606
00:35:32,880 --> 00:35:35,591
<i>Elle is right. Max should rest now.</i>

607
00:35:36,843 --> 00:35:38,302
<i>[phone vibrating]</i>

608
00:35:38,386 --> 00:35:39,428
<i>Hold on.</i>

609
00:35:40,680 --> 00:35:43,015
<i>Oh! Uncle Boyet! Grandma Bhaves!</i>

610
00:35:43,099 --> 00:35:47,770
<i>My child! How are you?</i>
<i>We were so worried about you.</i>

611
00:35:47,854 --> 00:35:51,274
<i>C'mon! This is nothing. Look!</i>

612
00:35:51,357 --> 00:35:53,067
<i>Barely a scratch!</i>

613
00:35:53,151 --> 00:35:55,862
<i>Poor child!</i>

614
00:35:55,945 --> 00:35:57,321
<i>Grandma.</i>

615
00:35:57,405 --> 00:35:58,739
<i>[Boyet]</i> Who head banged you?

616
00:35:58,823 --> 00:36:01,075
<i>That move only belongs</i>
<i>in a wrestling match.</i>

617
00:36:01,159 --> 00:36:03,327
<i>What kind of elite school do you go to?</i>

618
00:36:03,411 --> 00:36:05,246
<i>-I'll be fine, Uncle!</i>
<i>-Max.</i>

619
00:36:05,329 --> 00:36:08,457
<i>[Boyet] </i>Who hurt you? I'm gonna beat up
that lowlife! Going to Manila right now!

620
00:36:08,541 --> 00:36:10,418
<i>Boyet. This is Maxim.</i>

621
00:36:10,501 --> 00:36:12,170
<i>Hi. I didn't know you were there.</i>

622
00:36:12,837 --> 00:36:14,088
<i>[Maxim] </i>About what happened,

623
00:36:14,172 --> 00:36:16,299
<i>I'll make sure this won't happen again,</i>

624
00:36:16,382 --> 00:36:19,135
<i>and that whoever did this</i>
<i>will be held accountable.</i>

625
00:36:19,218 --> 00:36:21,053
<i>Good, good.</i>

626
00:36:21,137 --> 00:36:22,763
<i>Uh… sir.</i>

627
00:36:23,973 --> 00:36:27,685
<i>We would like to thank you</i>

628
00:36:27,768 --> 00:36:30,730
<i>for the money and for the medicine.</i>

629
00:36:31,314 --> 00:36:33,232
<i>Uh, we appreciate it.</i>

630
00:36:33,983 --> 00:36:35,193
<i>Thank you.</i>

631
00:36:35,776 --> 00:36:37,361
<i>No problem. Here's Max.</i>

632
00:36:39,989 --> 00:36:42,325
<i>Calm down.</i>
<i>You went into beast mode right away.</i>

633
00:36:42,408 --> 00:36:45,286
